The '''1996 Dubai Tennis Championships''' was a [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Hardcourt|outdoor hard courts]] at the [[Aviation Club Tennis Centre]] in [[Dubai]] in the [[United Arab Emirates]] and was part of the [[ATP International Series|World Series]] of the [[1996 ATP Tour]]. The tournament ran from February 12 through February 18, 1996.

==Winners==
===Men's Singles===
{{main|1996 Dubai Tennis Championships &ndash; Singles}}
{{flagicon|CRO}} '''[[Goran Ivanišević]]''' defeated {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Albert Costa]] 6&ndash;4, 6&ndash;3
* It was Ivanišević's 2nd title of the year and the 20th of his career.

===Men's Doubles===
{{main|1996 Dubai Tennis Championships &ndash; Doubles}}
{{flagicon|ZIM}} '''[[Byron Black]]''' / {{flagicon|CAN}} '''[[Grant Connell]]''' defeated {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Karel Nováček]] / {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Jiří Novák]] 6&ndash;0, 6&ndash;1
* It was Black's 1st title of the year and the 12th of his career. It was Connell's 1st title of the year and the 18th of his career.

