{{Infobox Athleticrace | date = April 15 | location = [[Daegu]], [[South Korea]] | type = Road | distance = [[Marathon]] - 10K - 5K | homepage = [http://marathon.daegusports.or.kr Daegu Marathon] }}
The '''Daegu International Marathon''' is an annual [[marathon]] race which takes place in April in [[Daegu]], [[South Korea]]. The day's events also feature a 5K event and a 10K event, as well as the full course marathon (42.195&nbsp;km).
The race begins and ends at the [[Daegu Stadium]]. A comparatively fast course, it hosted the [[2011 World Championships in Athletics|World Championships Marathon]] in September 2011.<ref>Jalava, Mirko (2011-04-11). [http://www.iaaf.org/WCH11/news/kind=100/newsid=59731.html Course records fall at Daegu Marathon]. [[IAAF]]. Retrieved on 2011-04-12.</ref>
