'''Juventus Manica''', usually known simply as '''Juventus Manica''', is a traditional [[football (soccer)]] club based in Manico, [[Mozambique]].

==Stadium==
The club plays their home matches at [[Gaparinu des Manica]], which has a maximum capacity of 10,000 people.<ref name="stadium">
[http://www.worldstadiums.com/africa/countries/mozambique.shtml World Stadiums]</ref>

