{{Infobox football club | clubname = SC Catumbela| image = | fullname = Sport Clube da Catumbela| nickname = | founded = | ground = [[Estádio Municipal de Benguela]], [[Angola]]| capacity = ??| chairman = {{Flagicon|ANG}} ??| manager = {{Flagicon|ANG}} ??| league = ??| season =| position = ? | }}
'''Sport Clube da Catumbela''' is an [[Angola]]n [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Catumbela]] in western [[Angola]], south of [[Luanda]].
In 1945 the team has won the [[Girabola]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesa/angochamp.html|title=Angola - List of Champions|website=www.rsssf.com|access-date=2017-07-11}}</ref>
