'''Taipei City Dragons FC''', also known as TC Dragons, is a football club from [[Chinese Taipei]], also called [[Taiwan]] or [[Republic of China]]. It is one of the main [[association football]] clubs in [[Chinese Taipei]]. 2,000 capacity [[Tainan Football Field]] is their home stadium.

